{
  "stem": "717.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I don't even think we took furniture because there would be no room in my grandparents' apartment to put it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But all our belongings, clothes, everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we drove up our street, Konstantynowska, to Baluty, to my grandparents' house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I don't remember the arrival.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I just remember-- in my mind's eye-- I just remember sitting on top of the wagon on all that stuff.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I remember the filming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "That, I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I was even happy to look there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I was hoping that they would see me on the camera.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Quite possible that that film exists somewhere in an archive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we lived with our grandparents for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And this was quite an experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My grandfather, at that time, I remember him coming home crying one day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I saw my grandfather cry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The Germans called him in the street, and they cut his beard.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And to him, this was the greatest tragedy, you know, religious Jew to have his beard cut.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "He cried.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "My grandfather cried.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And another tragedy befell this family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "He had a son, a younger son, my mother's youngest brother, Jochanan.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I think he-- he wasn't much older than me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I was 12.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And he was, I think, 17.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "But nevertheless, I called him uncle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can I go back a little bit to before the war?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just remembered an incident.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like I said, my parents weren't religious.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my grandmother sent him, this same son, she sent him to my mother for something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember what.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was Erev Pesach.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the day before Passover.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He came into our apartment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother was kneading a, a dough for cookies.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
